{"tid":2021231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：派發一萬元現金計劃「最快」六月底接受申請 七月中收錢！","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:18:00.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7d5606e8c0da9b6b25b2814824ef46f542fe43","tid":2021231,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94cea480d7d43533b194714736576525284dac0","tid":2021231,"uid":33872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"車厘"},{"pid":"9a50ed8300cea86bb9d400bdd12f1ac24a3c322f","tid":2021231,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBHccc6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBHccc6.png&h=6157a3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjvJiS8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjvJiS8.gif&h=f9f2b2d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4febe8288718f1fa3dc41600187f824a8e8ea4c5","tid":2021231,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:13:29.000Z","msg":"羅致光：社署若負責派1萬工作會令工作崩潰<br />\n17.05.2020 09:26<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局長羅致光在網誌提及派發一萬元現金計劃，指如果能透過社保制度派一萬元，可為政府省去約億元的行政費，但近月申請綜援個案倍增，社署社會保障部工作，正面對前所未有的壓力，若再加上派一萬元的工作，將會是最後一根稻草，令社署工作崩潰。作為局長不可能要求社署同事放緩處理綜援申請，或是其他同樣重要的工作，以進行派一萬元的工作，這個政治壓力會由他自己一力承擔。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光解釋，如果以社保制度派錢，最快七月後才有時間調校系統，社署可能要處理過千個查詢及過百個投訴，指俗語有云「說易行難」，做人「老闆」慎勿「隨口噏當秘笈」、「講一句、做死人」，問責官員須與同事探討政策與執行可行性，聆聽有何實際困難。民建聯主席李慧琼日前指，曾提出政府應利用現有津貼發放機制，向曾提交銀行戶口資料的市民派錢，但引述財政司長陳茂波重申勞福局不接納，批評羅致光「離地」，對他極度極度遺憾，要對他作出最嚴厲的警告。"},{"pid":"06b7d03042bebca040c0773e13ef733b89445f05","tid":2021231,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"學澳門一人一張支票好撚過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8ce33f7e8843f80f118b38d92d7d159de1ff20","tid":2021231,"uid":111019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"靠政府班廢柴半個月派到?我就唔撚信"},{"pid":"1274240993be5b46a4a7885a8444b14a669aa86f","tid":2021231,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"要趕及今年9月前派到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e22445276b38e6c44274d8f1c9322d5b280c9a0","tid":2021231,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃店捱多一個月呀<br />\n辛苦哂</span></strong>"},{"pid":"665dabdda3be879d3b72d04c743885c44316c7e3","tid":2021231,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"快啦就餓死"},{"pid":"0836cb965a011c03a3c8feeb7da7136dc8c462d7","tid":2021231,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:16:42.000Z","msg":"疫症完左啦<br />\n派唔派都無所謂"},{"pid":"fdc69a692f1c9f4f8009cb27475c5811b9f0e156","tid":2021231,"uid":1580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:18:00.000Z","msg":"個填表岩岩先寫完UAT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個月後先慢慢開始用"}]}